                <h1 class="h1Header"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right blue"></span> About OAS</h1>
                <h3 style="text-align:center; color:#AAA; font-style:italic; padding:0px 60px 20px 60px;">“ofPartner’s OAS allows you to quickly see how attorneys and support staff spend their time, and what it is costing the firm.”</h3>
