        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-sm-7">
                <p class="light">As a professional service provider, a law firm’s greatest assets are its people. With compensation one of the largest expenses, law firms simply cannot afford to mismanage this critical component of their business.</p>
                <p class="light">In response to this need, ofPartner Consulting Services has developed the <span class="blue"><strong>Organizational Assessment Survey (OAS)</strong></span>, a unique tool that provides leadership with unprecedented vision into a firm’s operation by analyzing the activities performed by each individual within the firm.</p>
                <p class="light">The <span class="blue"><strong>OAS</strong></span> does this using a simple online survey that asks respondents to describe the activities they perform during a typical year.</p>
                <p class="light">The result is an easy to use report that allows you to view and analyze your firm as a total organization, focusing on the functions performed, rather than positions held.</p>
                <p class="light">The report also allows you to filter the results to analyze individual offices, departments, practice groups, or employees. The survey and resulting data are organized into a logical structure that is intuitive and easy to follow. High-level technical experience is not necessary in order to effectively analyze your results.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-5">
                <p class="light blue"><strong>Who could utilize the OAS results?</strong></p>
